7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Krisp and Speechify share a solid foundation of core features including Real Time. Where Krisp pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Speech To Text and Noise Removal, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Speechify uniquely offers Text To Speech and Multilingual and Api Access, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Krisp holds an overall score of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Speechify scores 7/10 overall and 9/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Krisp offers a more budget-friendly entry point at $8/mo, compared to Speechify's starting price of $11.58/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Krisp's free tier and Speechify's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
